{"tid":2437781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"開明醫護三連勝 破建制壟斷","createTime":"2021-03-08T05:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T07:24:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39fce06fed4f736fcb1d4eb82e4ba4fc05db44e3","tid":2437781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:45:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/FPLOC32U7RAHLFAD3ECLJD63QA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FFPLOC32U7RAHLFAD3ECLJD63QA%2F&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058kYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=0a75e3d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210308%2FFPLOC32U7RAHLFAD3ECLJD63QA%2F&h=7070b3e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210308/FPLOC32U7RAHLFAD3ECLJD63QA/</a><br />\n<br />\n開明醫護三連勝 破建制壟斷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XJ_uTbTnoAOqJUzknzp-roTvbaQ=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q5IUAVKM4RAF3APLYD7SXAFVGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXJ_uTbTnoAOqJUzknzp-roTvbaQ%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ5IUAVKM4RAF3APLYD7SXAFVGI.jpg&h=6ee5ed08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■馬仲儀<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】近年不少醫護界組織或工會均打破由親政府人士壟斷的局面，換屆選舉先後由「黃營」或「開明派」大獲全勝，當中包括醫委會改選、醫學會會長及會董選舉。但面對政府紅線日漸收窄，在改選中獲勝的醫委會委員馬仲儀坦言有無力感，「當只求科學、公正都會被政府話政治掛帥，有時候都唔可以盡做到」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：創辦18年來首次  改革派贏深藍會長 西醫工會變天<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政治空間收窄 力守專業底線<br />\n<br />\n負責醫生發牌及投訴等事務的醫委會去年底改選三個直選委員席位，由被視為黃營的公共醫療醫生協會會長馬仲儀、前線醫生聯盟前副主席覃天笙及醫學會副會長鄭志文勝出，擊敗曾聯署撐警。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n除此以外，去年醫學會會長及會董選舉，被指屬建制的何仲平團隊同樣落敗，。。。。。。。。，大獲全勝。<br />\n<br />\n馬仲儀認為相關的變化受社運風潮，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n但她亦直言，以前港府或會聽取工會的意見，以追求。。。。。。"},{"pid":"7e049a67aae5596dc1696a0d12c1d49d565fe2cb","tid":2437781,"uid":71092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926959a384c275ef709f584a74f72fcda2f6500f","tid":2437781,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T06:41:50.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"7b3b294a96d9c660c8257dac97b6f8f1897f3b6f","tid":2437781,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bec49808916e3bd030234d29620836ebc5fb710","tid":2437781,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:24:54.000Z","msg":"又要完善選舉制度了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}